name: Phoenix
public_notice: Phoenix Global (PHB) has rebranded to Phoenix (PHB). For more information, please view this announcement on Twitter.

description.en: Phoenix is a Layer 1 and Layer 2 blockchain infrastructure, empowering intelligent Web3 applications, focusing on the next generation of AI & Privacy-Enabled Web3 Apps. Phoenix (PHB) is a cryptocurrency and operates on the BNB Smart Chain (BEP20) platform.
